plotting confidence intervals: alternative implementatinons

applying nonstandard evaluation in sampling from randomly selected
distributions (Davison)

tree structures and tree-recursive functions
Example: turn this R expression into tree-recursive!
Betas <- lapply(M, function(l3m) {
    df <- do.call(make.groups,
                  lapply(l3m,
                         function(l2m)
                             do.call(make.groups,
                                     lapply(l2m,
                                            get.estimate.CI, conf.lev = 0.99))))
